Package program

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IOCSV
    Imports and exports a CSV file
    Item
    This is the item class where it represent the item properties in the supermart store
    Manifest
    This classes is manifest where it represent a collection of trucks it will be used to generate manifest, and building CSV needed for importing it later on
    OrdinaryTruck
    OrdinaryTruck is a child from Truck class where it represent a truck that cannot have a temperature item inside of it
    RefrigratedTruck
    RefrigratedTruck is a child from Truck class where it represent a truck that can have a temperature item inside of it
    Stock
    Stock is a collection of item where it is used for method related with multiple item
    Store
    Store is the class that represent the SuperMart store where every method that related to changing inventory, capital of the store is in here
    Truck
    This class provides a skeletal implementation for the truck to minimize effort require to implement it in the refrigerated truck and ordinary truck
  • Exception Summary

    Throw CSV Format Exception Error
    DeliveryException
    Throw Delivery Exception
    StockException
    Throw Stock Exception
